	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've tried raw2chr and bmp2nes and they never work for me. Probably because I can't find any graphics software that will save in a 2 bit colour format. I even found software that would save in interleaved raw data from but never in 2 bits form. Any ideas? If I can't find anything, I'll code something that will take a .bmp with 4 colour bits but only 4 distinct colours and convert it into a .chr (interleaved 2 bitplane 8 pixel/2 byte graphics format). Does anybody know of any windows or DOS software that will import/draw and save to a 2 bit bitmap or a 2 bit colour interleaved RAW format? Thanks for any help.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


