		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've been working on something called "bmp2tiles" that takes an indexed image and turns it into tiles for any of several formats (1-bit, NES, GB, SNES, Genesis, GBA, etc), but I haven't yet had a chance to make a proper package of it. Want it?

		

