	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Doesn't seems to work good... I just got random pixels in output file.</div>
<br />Are you sure you used a 4-color indexed bitmap and that you specified <strong>-b nes</strong>? The proper command line looks like this:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">bmp2tiles -b nes tst.bmp tst.chr</div>
<br />
<br />Oh, and "nestc" isn't really all that trustable, as a lot of sites used "nestc" as the file name for some obsolete emulator that I don't need to mention here.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


